    "en": {
      "title": "Six more who attacked MP's houses are arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police headquarters said that six people including a woman were arrested for attacking and damaging the home offices and properties of the members of Parliament Arundika Fernando, Vidura Wickramanayake, Rohitha Abeygunawardena and Tharaka Balasuriya on May 9.",
        "The suspect was arrested for attacking Mr. Rohitha Abeygunawardena's house in Ratmalana.",
        "Mr. Arundika Fernando's house and office in Dankotuwa, Mr. Vidura Wickramanayake's Horana house, Mr. Tharaka Balasuriya's house in Kegalle. Others have been arrested for assault and damage."
      ],
